-that-they-did-not-enroll-in-the-normal-college-in-that-year-so-they-force-the-children-to-apply-for-the-normal-college-When-the-child-learns-broadcasting-host-he-insists-that-he-give-a-performance-to-his-uncle-and-aunt" class="headerlink" title="They regard their children as their own extension, and press their unfinished dreams on their children’s shoulders, and force them to do what they want them to do . When the children take the college entrance examination, they think that they did not enroll in the normal college in that year, so they force the children to apply for the normal college. When the child learns broadcasting host, he insists that he give a performance to his uncle and aunt."></a>They regard their children as their own extension, and press their unfinished dreams on their children’s shoulders, and force them to do what they want them to do . When the children take the college entrance examination, they think that they did not enroll in the normal college in that year, so they force the children to apply for the normal college. When the child learns broadcasting host, he insists that he give a performance to his uncle and aunt.</h6><h6 id="This-desire-for-ownership-and-control-is-not-only-embodied-in-children-but-also-in-children’s-possessions-so-children-have-no-privacy-they-must-to-read-their-children’s-diaries-cellphone-message-and-QQ-in-order-to-prevent-anything-bad-happens-So-children’s-toys-can-be-freely-given-away-no-matter-how-the-children-cry-parents-still-can-not-understand-“Is-a-broken-Teddy-bear-”-As-for-it-“-This-is-obviously-not-to-regard-children-as-independent-person-never-thinking-from-the-perspective-of-children-but-to-regard-their-values-as-natural"><a href="#This-desire-for-ownership-and-control-is-not-only-embodied-in-children-but-also-in-children’s-possessions-so-children-have-no-privacy-they-must-to-read-their-children’s-diaries-cellphone-message-and-QQ-in-order-to-prevent-anything-bad-happens-So-children’s-toys-can-be-freely-given-away-no-matter-how-the-children-cry-parents-still-can-not-understand-“Is-a-broken-Teddy-bear-”-As-for-it-“-This-is-obviously-not-to-regard-children-as-independent-person-never-thinking-from-the-perspective-of-children-but-to-regard-their-values-as-natural" class="headerlink" title="This desire for ownership and control is not only embodied in children, but also in children’s possessions, so children have no privacy, they must to read their children’s diaries , cellphone message and QQ, in order to prevent anything bad happens. So children’s toys can be freely given away, no matter how the children cry, parents still can not understand, “Is a broken Teddy bear?”  As for it ? “ This is obviously not to regard children as independent person, never thinking from the perspective of children, but to regard their values as natural."></a>This desire for ownership and control is not only embodied in children, but also in children’s possessions, so children have no privacy, they must to read their children’s diaries , cellphone message and QQ, in order to prevent anything bad happens. So children’s toys can be freely given away, no matter how the children cry, parents still can not understand, “Is a broken Teddy bear?”  As for it ? “ This is obviously not to regard children as independent person, never thinking from the perspective of children, but to regard their values as natural.</h6><h6 id="I’m-not-trying-to-prove-how-selfish-parents-are"><a href="#I’m-not-trying-to-prove-how-selfish-parents-are" class="headerlink" title="I’m not trying to prove how selfish parents are."></a>I’m not trying to prove how selfish parents are.</h6><h6 id="I-just-want-to-say-that-they-don’t-take-the-right-position-At-any-rate-they-child-is-not-an-accessory-to-you-they-can’t-just-walk-on-their-footprints-Because-all-healthy-and-good-relationships-between-people-in-the-world-are-based-on-equality-even-the-relationship-between-parents-and-children-should-be-based-on-equality-and-mutual-respect"><a href="#I-just-want-to-say-that-they-don’t-take-the-right-position-At-any-rate-they-child-is-not-an-accessory-to-you-they-can’t-just-walk-on-their-footprints-Because-all-healthy-and-good-relationships-between-people-in-the-world-are-based-on-equality-even-the-relationship-between-parents-and-children-should-be-based-on-equality-and-mutual-respect" class="headerlink" title="I just want to say that they don’t  take  the right position. At any rate, they child is not an accessory to you. they can’t just walk on their footprints. Because all healthy and good relationships between people in the world are based on equality, even the relationship between parents and children should be based on equality and mutual respect."></a>I just want to say that they don’t  take  the right position. At any rate, they child is not an accessory to you. they can’t just walk on their footprints. Because all healthy and good relationships between people in the world are based on equality, even the relationship between parents and children should be based on equality and mutual respect.</h6><h6 id="I-love-my-parents-very-much"><a href="#I-love-my-parents-very-much" class="headerlink" title="I love my parents very much."></a>I love my parents very much.</h6><h6 id="Although-they-are-ordinary-they-are-all-trying-to-love-me-in-their-way"><a href="#Although-they-are-ordinary-they-are-all-trying-to-love-me-in-their-way" class="headerlink" title="Although they are ordinary, they are all trying to love me in their way."></a>Although they are ordinary, they are all trying to love me in their way.</h6><h6 id="When-I-make-mistakes-they-point-out-and-sometimes-they-make-mistakes-and-I-often-communicate-with-them-our-feelings-improve-in-communication"><a href="#When-I-make-mistakes-they-point-out-and-sometimes-they-make-mistakes-and-I-often-communicate-with-them-our-feelings-improve-in-communication" class="headerlink" title="When I make mistakes, they point out, and sometimes they make mistakes, and I often communicate with them, our feelings improve in communication."></a>When I make mistakes, they point out, and sometimes they make mistakes, and I often communicate with them, our feelings improve in communication.</h6><h6 id="As-I-have-said-maybe-the-motivation-to-love-is-innate-but-feelings-are-nurtured-bit-by-bit-We-should-all-benefit-and-grow-in-this-process"><a href="#As-I-have-said-maybe-the-motivation-to-love-is-innate-but-feelings-are-nurtured-bit-by-bit-We-should-all-benefit-and-grow-in-this-process" class="headerlink" title="As I have said, maybe the motivation to love is innate, but feelings are nurtured bit by bit. We should all benefit and grow in this process."></a>As I have said, maybe the motivation to love is innate, but feelings are nurtured bit by bit. We should all benefit and grow in this process.</h6>]]></content>
    
